{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845692310,"sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","part":{"id":"prt_d78a6cd02001MdWTNaAjytlW7P","messageID":"msg_d78a6c2260015VM749XGmIy7Mh","sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-df994f0a51c44343a8d83178470cca4e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 Proposal\n2: \n3: [To be filled]\n\n(End of file - total 3 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 Proposal\n\n[To be filled]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775845692288,"end":1775845692309}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845692312,"sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","part":{"id":"prt_d78a6d364001xX3trD5jERPr3Q","messageID":"msg_d78a6c2260015VM749XGmIy7Mh","sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-9e27d46cf05d4866a756c9e88bacebce","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 实现 Sandbox 创建处理器（SandboxController），作为 WorkloadManager 的核心组件，负责基于 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 资源创建、管理和清理执行沙箱。该处理器通过创建 Sandbox CRD 实例来管理隔离的执行环境，并提供会话生命周期管理功能。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 平台提供 Sandbox 创建处理器，实现：\n10: - 基于 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 配置创建执行沙箱\n11: - 沙箱会话的生命周期管理（创建、查询、删除）\n12: - 沙箱状态跟踪和过期清理\n13: - 端点（entry point）暴露和管理\n14: - 与 Kubernetes 集成，使用 Sandbox CRD 管理执行环境\n15: \n16: ## Module\n17: \n18: `pkg/workloadmanager/controller`\n19: \n20: ## Language\n21: \n22: Go 1.24\n23: \n24: ## Size\n25: \n26: M\n27: \n28: ## Scope\n29: \n30: ### In Scope\n31: \n32: 1. **SandboxController 实现**\n33:    - `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 方法 - 为 AgentRuntime 创建沙箱\n34:    - `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 方法 - 为 CodeInterpreter 创建沙箱\n35:    - `GetSession` 方法 - 获取会话信息\n36:    - `DeleteSession` 方法 - 删除会话\n37: \n38: 2. **Sandbox CRD 构建**\n39:    - `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` - 构建 AgentRuntime 的 Sandbox CR\n40:    - `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` - 构建 CodeInterpreter 的 Sandbox CR\n41:    - 配置沙箱生命周期和标签\n42:    - 配置 pod 模板和端口\n43: \n44: 3. **会话管理**\n45:    - 会话 ID 生成\n46:    - 沙箱名称生成\n47:    - 沙箱状态跟踪（pending → running）\n48:    - 端点构建和返回\n49: \n50: 4. **存储集成**\n51:    - 使用 Redis Store 存储会话信息\n52:    - 会话过期管理\n53:    - 会话查询和删除\n54: \n55: 5. **Kubernetes 集成**\n56:    - 使用 client-go 创建 Sandbox CR\n57:    - 等待 Pod IP 分配\n58:    - 清理失败或过期的沙箱\n59: \n60: 6. **后台清理任务**\n61:    - 定期清理过期沙箱\n62:    - 定期清理不活跃沙箱\n63: \n64: ### Out of Scope\n65: \n66: - Sandbox CRD 的实现（已由 agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1 提供）\n67: - AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter Controller 的实现\n68: - 沙箱内部执行逻辑\n69: - HTTP Handler 层实现（由 handler 包负责）\n70: \n71: ## Impact Analysis\n72: \n73: ### Components Impacted\n74: \n75: 1. **WorkloadManager Server**\n76:    - 集成 SandboxController\n77:    - 提供沙箱创建 API 端点\n78:    - 启动后台清理任务\n79: \n80: 2. **Handler 层**\n81:    - `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` Handler - 调用 controller 方法\n82:    - `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` Handler - 调用 controller 方法\n83:    - `GetSession` Handler\n84:    - `DeleteSession` Handler\n85: \n86: 3. **K8sClient**\n87:    - 需要支持 Sandbox CR 的创建、删除和查询\n88:    - 需要支持获取 Pod IP\n89: \n90: 4. **Redis Store**\n91:    - 存储 SandboxInfo\n92:    - 查询和删除会话\n93:    - 列出过期和不活跃沙箱\n94: \n95: 5. **RBAC**\n96:    - 需要创建 Sandbox 资源的权限\n97:    - 需要删除 Sandbox 资源的权限\n98:    - 需要查询 Pod 的权限\n99: \n100: ### Dependencies\n101: \n102: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` - Kubernetes 客户端\n103: - `github.com/google/uuid` - UUID 生成\n104: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured` - Unstructured 类型处理\n105: - `k8s.io/api/core/v1` - 核心 API 类型\n106: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store` - 存储接口\n107: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` - 公共类型\n108: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/api` - API 类型定义\n109: \n110: ## Design Decisions\n111: \n112: ### 沙箱名称生成策略\n113: \n114: **选择**: `{workloadName}-{randomSuffix}` 格式\n115: \n116: **理由**:\n117: - 便于识别来源工作负载\n118: - 随机后缀避免命名冲突\n119: - 符合 Kubernetes 资源命名规范\n120: \n121: **示例**: `my-agent-abc12345`\n122: \n123: ### 会话超时策略\n124: \n125: **选择**:\n126: - 沙箱默认过期时间：8 小时\n127: - 空闲超时（annotation）：15 分钟\n128: \n129: **理由**:\n130: - 8 小时覆盖典型工作会话\n131: - 15 分钟空闲超时避免资源浪费\n132: - 平衡资源利用和用户体验\n133: \n134: ### Pod IP 等待策略\n135: \n136: **选择**: 轮询等待，最多 2 分钟，间隔 2 秒\n137: \n138: **理由**:\n139: - 简单可靠\n140: - 2 分钟足够大多数场景\n141: - 超时后自动清理，避免资源泄漏\n142: \n143: ### 错误处理策略\n144: \n145: **选择**: 失败即清理（fail-and-cleanup）\n146: \n147: **理由**:\n148: - 避免部分成功的资源残留\n149: - 确保系统状态一致性\n150: - 简化错误恢复逻辑\n151: \n152: **实现**:\n153: - 任何步骤失败后，删除已创建的 Sandbox CR\n154: - 删除 Store 中的会话记录\n155: \n156: ### 端点构建策略\n157: \n158: **选择**: 基于 Pod IP 和 spec.ports 构建\n159: \n160: **理由**:\n161: - Pod IP 是集群内部访问点\n162: - 从配置中读取端口信息\n163: - 支持多端口场景\n164: \n165: ### 后台清理策略\n166: \n167: **选择**: 定时任务，每分钟清理过期和不活跃沙箱\n168: \n169: **理由**:\n170: - 定期检查保持资源清理\n171: - 不影响主请求性能\n172: - 简单可靠\n173: \n174: ## Alternatives Considered\n175: \n176: ### Alternative 1: 使用事件驱动清理\n177: \n178: **描述**: 监听 Sandbox CR 事件，基于状态变化触发清理\n179: \n180: **优点**:\n181: - 实时响应\n182: - 减少定期扫描开销\n183: \n184: **缺点**:\n185: - 增加复杂度\n186: - 依赖 Kubernetes 事件机制\n187: - 可能遗漏不活跃沙箱\n188: \n189: **选择**: 不采纳 - 定时任务更简单可靠\n190: \n191: ### Alternative 2: 使用 Informer 监听沙箱状态\n192: \n193: **描述**: 使用 SharedInformerFactory 监听 Sandbox CR 变化\n194: \n195: **优点**:\n196: - 实时状态更新\n197: - 本地缓存提高性能\n198: \n199: **缺点**:\n200: - 增加内存使用\n201: - Informer 同步延迟\n202: - 当前实现已经满足需求\n203: \n204: **选择**: 不采纳 - 直接查询已足够\n205: \n206: ### Alternative 3: 支持自定义超时配置\n207: \n208: **描述**: 允许在请求中指定超时时间\n209: \n210: **优点**:\n211: - 更灵活\n212: \n213: **缺点**:\n214: - 增加验证复杂度\n215: - 可能导致资源滥用\n216: \n217: **选择**: 不采纳 - 使用固定超时值更安全\n218: \n219: ### Alternative 4: 异步创建沙箱\n220: \n221: **描述**: 立即返回 session ID，后台异步创建沙箱\n222: \n223: **优点**:\n224: - 更快的响应时间\n225: \n226: **缺点**:\n227: - 客户端需要轮询状态\n228: - 增加复杂度\n229: - 可能影响用户体验\n230: \n231: **选择**: 不采纳 - 同步创建更简单\n232: \n233: ## Implementation Plan\n234: \n235: ### Phase 1: 基础结构 (Day 1)\n236: \n237: 1. 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go`\n238: 2. 定义 `SandboxController` 结构体\n239: 3. 实现 `NewSandboxController` 构造函数\n240: 4. 实现辅助方法：\n241:    - `generateSandboxName`\n242:    - `RandString`\n243: \n244: ### Phase 2: Sandbox CR 构建 (Day 1-2)\n245: \n246: 1. 实现 `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`\n247:    - 设置 APIVersion 和 Kind\n248:    - 设置名称和命名空间\n249:    - 设置标签和注解\n250:    - 配置 spec（replicas、lifecycle、podTemplate、ports）\n251: \n252: 2. 实现 `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR`\n253:    - 类似 AgentRuntime\n254:    - 配置默认镜像\n255:    - 配置 podTemplate\n256: \n257: 3. 实现 `buildEntryPoints`\n258:    - 基于 Pod IP 和端口配置构建端点列表\n259: \n260: ### Phase 3: 沙箱创建逻辑 (Day 2-3)\n261: \n262: 1. 实现 `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`\n263:    - 验证 AgentRuntime 存在\n264:    - 生成会话 ID 和沙箱名称\n265:    - 构建 Sandbox CR\n266:    - 存储会话信息到 Redis\n267:    - 创建 Sandbox CR\n268:    - 等待 Pod IP 分配\n269:    - 构建端点信息\n270:    - 更新会话状态\n271:    - 返回响应\n272: \n273: 2. 实现 `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`\n274:    - 类似 AgentRuntime\n275:    - 配置默认端口\n276: \n277: ### Phase 4: 会话管理 (Day 3)\n278: \n279: 1. 实现 `GetSession`\n280:    - 从 Store 获取会话信息\n281:    - 返回会话详情\n282: \n283: 2. 实现 `DeleteSession`\n284:    - 获取会话信息\n285:    - 删除 Kubernetes 中的 Sandbox CR\n286:    - 删除 Store 中的会话记录\n287: \n288: ### Phase 5: 辅助函数 (Day 3)\n289: \n290: 1. 实现 `convertEntryPoints`\n291: 2. 实现 `convertToAPIEntryPoints`\n292: \n293: ### Phase 6: 后台清理任务 (Day 4)\n294: \n295: 1. 在 Server 中集成 SandboxController\n296: 2. 实现定期清理过期沙箱任务\n297: 3. 实现定期清理不活跃沙箱任务\n298: 4. 配置清理间隔和批量大小\n299: \n300: ### Phase 7: K8sClient 扩展 (Day 4-5)\n301: \n302: 1. 实现 `CreateSandbox` 方法\n303: 2. 实现 `DeleteSandbox` 方法\n304: 3. 实现 `GetPodIP` 方法\n305: 4. 实现 `GetAgentRuntime` 方法\n306: 5. 实现 `GetCodeInterpreter` 方法\n307: \n308: ### Phase 8: Handler 集成 (Day 5)\n309: \n310: 1. 更新 `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` Handler\n311: 2. 更新 `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` Handler\n312: 3. 实现 `GetSession` Handler\n313: 4. 实现 `DeleteSession` Handler\n314: \n315: ### Phase 9: 测试 (Day 5-6)\n316: \n317: 1. 单元测试\n318:    - 测试 Sandbox CR 构建\n319:    - 测试沙箱创建逻辑\n320:    - 测试会话管理\n321:    - 测试辅助函数\n322: \n323: 2. 集成测试\n324:    - 测试端到端沙箱创建\n325:    - 测试过期清理\n326:    - 测试错误场景\n327: \n328: 3. 性能测试\n329:    - 测试并发创建\n330:    - 测试资源使用\n331: \n332: ### Phase 10: 文档 (Day 6)\n333: \n334: 1. 添加代码注释\n335: 2. 更新 API 文档\n336: 3. 添加使用示例\n337: \n338: ## Testing Strategy\n339: \n340: ### Unit Tests\n341: \n342: 1. **SandboxController 测试**\n343:    - 测试 `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`\n344:    - 测试 `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`\n345:    - 测试 `GetSession`\n346:    - 测试 `DeleteSession`\n347: \n348: 2. **Sandbox CR 构建测试**\n349:    - 验证 CR 结构正确\n350:    - 验证标签和注解正确\n351:    - 验证 spec 配置正确\n352: \n353: 3. **辅助函数测试**\n354:    - 测试名称生成\n355:    - 测试端点构建\n356:    - 测试类型转换\n357: \n358: 4. **错误处理测试**\n359:    - 测试 AgentRuntime 不存在\n360:    - 测试 CodeInterpreter 不存在\n361:    - 测试超时场景\n362:    - 测试失败清理\n363: \n364: ### Integration Tests\n365: \n366: 1. **Kubernetes 集成测试**\n367:    - 创建真实的 Sandbox CR\n368:    - 验证 Pod 创建\n369:    - 验证 IP 分配\n370: \n371: 2. **端到端测试**\n372:    - 通过 API 创建沙箱\n373:    - 查询会话信息\n374:    - 删除会话\n375:    - 验证资源清理\n376: \n377: 3. **清理任务测试**\n378:    - 创建过期沙箱\n379:    - 验证定时清理\n380:    - 创建不活跃沙箱\n381:    - 验证定时清理\n382: \n383: ### Test Coverage\n384: \n385: 目标：> 80% 代码覆盖率\n386: \n387: ## API Specification\n388: \n389: ### Create AgentRuntime Sandbox\n390: \n391: ```\n392: POST /api/v1/sandboxes/agent-runtime\n393: Content-Type: application/json\n394: \n395: {\n396:   \"name\": \"my-agent-runtime\",\n397:   \"namespace\": \"default\"\n398: }\n399: \n400: Response:\n401: {\n402:   \"sessionId\": \"uuid\",\n403:   \"sandboxId\": \"sandbox-uid\",\n404:   \"sandboxName\": \"my-agent-runtime-abc12345\",\n405:   \"entryPoints\": [\n406:     {\n407:       \"protocol\": \"HTTP\",\n408:       \"endpoint\": \"10.244.1.5:8080\",\n409:       \"path\": \"/api\",\n410:       \"port\": 8080\n411:     }\n412:   ],\n413:   \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n414:   \"expiresAt\": \"2024-01-01T08:00:00Z\"\n415: }\n416: ```\n417: \n418: ### Create CodeInterpreter Sandbox\n419: \n420: ```\n421: POST /api/v1/sandboxes/code-interpreter\n422: Content-Type: application/json\n423: \n424: {\n425:   \"name\": \"python-interpreter\",\n426:   \"namespace\": \"default\"\n427: }\n428: \n429: Response:\n430: {\n431:   \"sessionId\": \"uuid\",\n432:   \"sandboxId\": \"sandbox-uid\",\n433:   \"sandboxName\": \"python-interpreter-def67890\",\n434:   \"entryPoints\": [\n435:     {\n436:       \"protocol\": \"HTTP\",\n437:       \"endpoint\": \"10.244.1.6:8080\",\n438:       \"path\": \"\",\n439:       \"port\": 8080\n440:     }\n441:   ],\n442:   \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n443:   \"expiresAt\": \"2024-01-01T08:00:00Z\"\n444: }\n445: ```\n446: \n447: ### Get Session\n448: \n449: ```\n450: GET /api/v1/sessions/{sessionId}\n451: \n452: Response:\n453: {\n454:   \"sessionId\": \"uuid\",\n455:   \"sandboxId\": \"sandbox-uid\",\n456:   \"sandboxName\": \"my-agent-runtime-abc12345\",\n457:   \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n458:   \"namespace\": \"default\",\n459:   \"name\": \"my-agent-runtime\",\n460:   \"entryPoints\": [...],\n461:   \"lastActivity\": \"2024-01-01T00:05:00Z\",\n462:   \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n463:   \"expiresAt\": \"2024-01-01T08:00:00Z\",\n464:   \"podIp\": \"10.244.1.5\"\n465: }\n466: ```\n467: \n468: ### Delete Session\n469: \n470: ```\n471: DELETE /api/v1/sessions/{sessionId}\n472: \n473: Response:\n474: {\n475:   \"sessionId\": \"uuid\",\n476:   \"deletedAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:10:00Z\"\n477: }\n478: ```\n479: \n480: ## Security Considerations\n481: \n482: 1. **资源隔离**\n483:    - 每个 Sandbox 运行在独立的 Pod 中\n484:    - 使用 Kubernetes 原生资源隔离\n485: \n486: 2. **会话安全**\n487:    - 使用 UUID 作为会话 ID\n488:    - 会话 ID 不可预测\n489: \n490: 3. **资源清理**\n491:    - 确保失败时清理资源\n492:    - 定期清理过期沙箱\n493: \n494: 4. **输入验证**\n495:    - 验证工作负载存在\n496:    - 验证命名空间存在\n497:    - 验证权限\n498: \n499: ## Performance Considerations\n500: \n501: 1. **并发创建**\n502:    - 使用 goroutine 并发处理\n503:    - 限制并发数量\n504: \n505: 2. **缓存策略**\n506:    - 会话信息存储在 Redis\n507:    - 快速查询响应\n508: \n509: 3. **资源清理**\n510:    - 批量清理减少开销\n511:    - 定期任务避免阻塞主流程\n512: \n513: 4. **超时控制**\n514:    - Pod IP 等待超时\n515:    - 请求上下文超时\n516: \n517: ## Open Questions\n518: \n519: 1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持沙箱更新？\n520:    - **当前**: 不支持\n521:    - **讨论**: 可能需要更新沙箱配置\n522:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n523: \n524: 2. **Q2**: 是否需要支持沙箱扩容？\n525:    - **当前**: 固定 1 个 replica\n526:    - **讨论**: 高负载场景可能需要多副本\n527:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n528: \n529: 3. **Q3**: 是否需要记录会话活动？\n530:    - **当前**: 仅记录最后活动时间\n531:    - **讨论**: 可能需要详细的活动日志\n532:    - **决策**: 初始仅记录最后活动时间\n533: \n534: 4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持会话续期？\n535:    - **当前**: 固定 8 小时过期\n536:    - **讨论**: 长会话可能需要续期\n537:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n538: \n539: ## Next Steps\n540: \n541: 1. 完善 K8sClient 实现\n542: 2. 编写单元测试\n543: 3. 编写集成测试\n544: 4. 性能测试和优化\n545: 5. 更新文档\n546: \n547: ## References\n548: \n549: - [Kubernetes API Conventions](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md)\n550: - [AgentCube Design Document](../deployment/design.md)\n551: - [AgentCube Specification](../deployment/spec.md)\n552: - [client-go library documentation](./deployment/client-go.md)\n553: - [Sandbox CRD Specification](https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/sandbox-api)\n\n(End of file - total 553 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 Sandbox 创建处理器（SandboxController），作为 WorkloadManager 的核心组件，负责基于 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 资源创建、管理和清理执行沙箱。该处理器通过创建 Sandbox CRD 实例来管理隔离的执行环境，并提供会话生命周期管理功能。\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 平台提供 Sandbox 创建处理器，实现：\n- 基于 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 配置创建执行沙箱\n- 沙箱会话的生命周期管理（创建、查询、删除）\n- 沙箱状态跟踪和过期清理\n- 端点（entry point）暴露和管理\n- 与 Kubernetes 集成，使用 Sandbox CRD 管理执行环境\n\n## Module\n\n`pkg/workloadmanager/controller`\n\n## Language","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775845692295,"end":1775845692310}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845692316,"sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","part":{"id":"prt_d78a6d113001VrFEfK9oMUasKL","messageID":"msg_d78a6c2260015VM749XGmIy7Mh","sessionID":"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-849fef5212ea4c4d9c5b4a7a388c8ef7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package controller\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"fmt\"\n6: \t\"math/rand\"\n7: \t\"time\"\n8: \n9: \t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n10: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n11: \tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n12: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured\"\n13: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n14: \n15: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/constants\"\n16: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n17: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\"\n18: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/api\"\n19: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/client\"\n20: )\n21: \n22: type Controller interface {\n23: \tCreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(ctx context.Context, req *api.CreateSandboxRequest) (*api.CreateSandboxResponse, error)\n24: \tCreateCodeInterpreterSandbox(ctx context.Context, req *api.CreateSandboxRequest) (*api.CreateSandboxResponse, error)\n25: \tGetSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*api.GetSessionResponse, error)\n26: \tDeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*api.DeleteSessionResponse, error)\n27: }\n28: \n29: type SandboxController struct {\n30: \tk8sClient client.Client\n31: \tstore     store.Store\n32: }\n33: \n34: func NewSandboxController(k8sClient client.Client, store store.Store) *SandboxController {\n35: \treturn &SandboxController{\n36: \t\tk8sClient: k8sClient,\n37: \t\tstore:     store,\n38: \t}\n39: }\n40: \n41: func (sc *SandboxController) CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(ctx context.Context, req *api.CreateSandboxRequest) (*api.CreateSandboxResponse, error) {\n42: \tagentRuntime, err := sc.k8sClient.GetAgentRuntime(ctx, req.Namespace, req.Name)\n43: \tif err != nil {\n44: \t\tif apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n45: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"AgentRuntime %s/%s not found\", req.Namespace, req.Name)\n46: \t\t}\n47: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get AgentRuntime: %w\", err)\n48: \t}\n49: \n50: \tspec, found, err := unstructured.NestedMap(agentRuntime.Object, \"spec\")\n51: \tif err != nil {\n52: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get spec: %w\", err)\n53: \t}\n54: \tif !found {\n55: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"spec not found\")\n56: \t}\n57: \n58: \tsessionID := uuid.New().String()\n59: \tsandboxName := generateSandboxName(req.Name)\n60: \n61: \tsandboxCR, err := sc.buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR(agentRuntime, sessionID, sandboxName, req.Name, req.Namespace)\n62: \tif err != nil {\n63: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to build sandbox CR: %w\", err)\n64: \t}\n65: \n66: \tsandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n67: \t\tSessionID:    sessionID,\n68: \t\tSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n69: \t\tWorkloadName: req.Name,\n70: \t\tNamespace:    req.Namespace,\n71: \t\tKind:         \"AgentRuntime\",\n72: \t\tStatus:       \"pending\",\n73: \t\tCreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n74: \t\tExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour),\n75: \t}\n76: \n77: \tif err := sc.store.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n78: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to store sandbox: %w\", err)\n79: \t}\n80: \n81: \tcreatedCR, err := sc.k8sClient.CreateSandbox(ctx, req.Namespace, sandboxCR)\n82: \tif err != nil {\n83: \t\tsc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n84: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to create sandbox: %w\", err)\n85: \t}\n86: \n87: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, 2*time.Minute)\n88: \tdefer cancel()\n89: \n90: \tvar podIP string\n91: \tfor i := 0; i < 60; i++ {\n92: \t\tpodIP, err = sc.k8sClient.GetPodIP(ctx, sandboxName, req.Namespace, createdCR)\n93: \t\tif err == nil {\n94: \t\t\tbreak\n95: \t\t}\n96: \t\tselect {\n97: \t\tcase <-ctx.Done():\n98: \t\t\tsc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n99: \t\t\tsc.k8sClient.DeleteSandbox(ctx, req.Namespace, sandboxName)\n100: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"sandbox creation timed out\")\n101: \t\tcase <-time.After(2 * time.Second):\n102: \t\t\tcontinue\n103: \t\t}\n104: \t}\n105: \n106: \tports, _, err := unstructured.NestedSlice(spec, \"ports\")\n107: \tif err != nil {\n108: \t\tsc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n109: \t\tsc.k8sClient.DeleteSandbox(ctx, req.Namespace, sandboxName)\n110: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get ports: %w\", err)\n111: \t}\n112: \n113: \tentryPoints := sc.buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)\n114: \n115: \tsandboxInfo.SandboxID = string(createdCR.GetUID())\n116: \tsandboxInfo.PodIP = podIP\n117: \tsandboxInfo.EntryPoints = convertEntryPoints(entryPoints)\n118: \tsandboxInfo.Status = \"running\"\n119: \n120: \tif err := sc.store.UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n121: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to update sandbox: %w\", err)\n122: \t}\n123: \n124: \treturn &api.CreateSandboxResponse{\n125: \t\tSessionID:   sessionID,\n126: \t\tSandboxID:   sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n127: \t\tSandboxName: sandboxName,\n128: \t\tEntryPoints: entryPoints,\n129: \t\tCreatedAt:   sandboxInfo.CreatedAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n130: \t\tExpiresAt:   sandboxInfo.ExpiresAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n131: \t}, nil\n132: }\n133: \n134: func (sc *SandboxController) CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox(ctx context.Context, req *api.CreateSandboxRequest) (*api.CreateSandboxResponse, error) {\n135: \tcodeInterpreter, err := sc.k8sClient.GetCodeInterpreter(ctx, req.Namespace, req.Name)\n136: \tif err != nil {\n137: \t\tif apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n138: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"CodeInterpreter %s/%s not found\", req.Namespace, req.Name)\n139: \t\t}\n140: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get CodeInterpreter: %w\", err)\n141: \t}\n142: \n143: \tspec, found, err := unstructured.NestedMap(codeInterpreter.Object, \"spec\")\n144: \tif err != nil {\n145: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get spec: %w\", err)\n146: \t}\n147: \tif !found {\n148: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"spec not found\")\n149: \t}\n150: \n151: \tsessionID := uuid.New().String()\n152: \tsandboxName := generateSandboxName(req.Name)\n153: \n154: \tports, _, _ := unstructured.NestedSlice(spec, \"ports\")\n155: \tif len(ports) == 0 {\n156: \t\tports = []interface{}{\n157: \t\t\tmap[string]interface{}{\n158: \t\t\t\t\"port\":     int64(8080),\n159: \t\t\t\t\"protocol\": \"HTTP\",\n160: \t\t\t},\n161: \t\t}\n162: \t}\n163: \n164: \tsandboxCR, err := sc.buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(codeInterpreter, sessionID, sandboxName, req.Name, req.Namespace, ports)\n165: \tif err != nil {\n166: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to build sandbox CR: %w\", err)\n167: \t}\n168: \n169: \tsandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n170: \t\tSessionID:    sessionID,\n171: \t\tSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n172: \t\tWorkloadName: req.Name,\n173: \t\tNamespace:    req.Namespace,\n174: \t\tKind:         \"CodeInterpreter\",\n175: \t\tStatus:       \"pending\",\n176: \t\tCreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n177: \t\tExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour),\n178: \t}\n179: \n180: \tif err := sc.store.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n181: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to store sandbox: %w\", err)\n182: \t}\n183: \n184: \tcreatedCR, err := sc.k8sClient.CreateSandbox(ctx, req.Namespace, sandboxCR)\n185: \tif err != nil {\n186: \t\tsc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n187: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to create sandbox: %w\", err)\n188: \t}\n189: \n190: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, 2*time.Minute)\n191: \tdefer cancel()\n192: \n193: \tvar podIP string\n194: \tfor i := 0; i < 60; i++ {\n195: \t\tpodIP, err = sc.k8sClient.GetPodIP(ctx, sandboxName, req.Namespace, createdCR)\n196: \t\tif err == nil {\n197: \t\t\tbreak\n198: \t\t}\n199: \t\tselect {\n200: \t\tcase <-ctx.Done():\n201: \t\t\tsc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n202: \t\t\tsc.k8sClient.DeleteSandbox(ctx, req.Namespace, sandboxName)\n203: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"sandbox creation timed out\")\n204: \t\tcase <-time.After(2 * time.Second):\n205: \t\t\tcontinue\n206: \t\t}\n207: \t}\n208: \n209: \tentryPoints := sc.buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)\n210: \n211: \tsandboxInfo.SandboxID = string(createdCR.GetUID())\n212: \tsandboxInfo.PodIP = podIP\n213: \tsandboxInfo.EntryPoints = convertEntryPoints(entryPoints)\n214: \tsandboxInfo.Status = \"running\"\n215: \n216: \tif err := sc.store.UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n217: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to update sandbox: %w\", err)\n218: \t}\n219: \n220: \treturn &api.CreateSandboxResponse{\n221: \t\tSessionID:   sessionID,\n222: \t\tSandboxID:   sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n223: \t\tSandboxName: sandboxName,\n224: \t\tEntryPoints: entryPoints,\n225: \t\tCreatedAt:   sandboxInfo.CreatedAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n226: \t\tExpiresAt:   sandboxInfo.ExpiresAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n227: \t}, nil\n228: }\n229: \n230: func (sc *SandboxController) GetSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*api.GetSessionResponse, error) {\n231: \tsandboxInfo, err := sc.store.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)\n232: \tif err != nil {\n233: \t\tif err == store.ErrNotFound {\n234: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"session not found\")\n235: \t\t}\n236: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get session: %w\", err)\n237: \t}\n238: \n239: \treturn &api.GetSessionResponse{\n240: \t\tSessionID:    sandboxInfo.SessionID,\n241: \t\tSandboxID:    sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n242: \t\tSandboxName:  sandboxInfo.SandboxName,\n243: \t\tKind:         sandboxInfo.Kind,\n244: \t\tNamespace:    sandboxInfo.Namespace,\n245: \t\tName:         sandboxInfo.WorkloadName,\n246: \t\tEntryPoints:  convertToAPIEntryPoints(sandboxInfo.EntryPoints),\n247: \t\tLastActivity: sandboxInfo.LastActivityAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n248: \t\tCreatedAt:    sandboxInfo.CreatedAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n249: \t\tExpiresAt:    sandboxInfo.ExpiresAt.Format(time.RFC3339),\n250: \t\tPodIP:        sandboxInfo.PodIP,\n251: \t}, nil\n252: }\n253: \n254: func (sc *SandboxController) DeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*api.DeleteSessionResponse, error) {\n255: \tsandboxInfo, err := sc.store.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)\n256: \tif err != nil {\n257: \t\tif err == store.ErrNotFound {\n258: \t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"session not found\")\n259: \t\t}\n260: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get session: %w\", err)\n261: \t}\n262: \n263: \tif err := sc.k8sClient.DeleteSandbox(ctx, sandboxInfo.Namespace, sandboxInfo.SandboxName); err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n264: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to delete sandbox: %w\", err)\n265: \t}\n266: \n267: \tif err := sc.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID); err != nil {\n268: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to delete session: %w\", err)\n269: \t}\n270: \n271: \treturn &api.DeleteSessionResponse{\n272: \t\tSessionID: sessionID,\n273: \t\tDeletedAt: time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n274: \t}, nil\n275: }\n276: \n277: func (sc *SandboxController) buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR(agentRuntime *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error) {\n278: \tcr := &unstructured.Unstructured{}\n279: \tcr.SetAPIVersion(\"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\")\n280: \tcr.SetKind(\"Sandbox\")\n281: \tcr.SetName(sandboxName)\n282: \tcr.SetNamespace(namespace)\n283: \n284: \tcr.SetLabels(map[string]string{\n285: \t\tconstants.LabelManagedBy:    constants.LabelManagedByValue,\n286: \t\tconstants.LabelSessionID:    sessionID,\n287: \t\tconstants.LabelWorkloadName: workloadName,\n288: \t\tconstants.LabelSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n289: \t})\n290: \n291: \tcr.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n292: \t\tconstants.AnnotationIdleTimeout: \"15m\",\n293: \t})\n294: \n295: \tshutdownTime := time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour)\n296: \n297: \tspec := map[string]interface{}{\n298: \t\t\"replicas\": int64(1),\n299: \t\t\"lifecycle\": map[string]interface{}{\n300: \t\t\t\"shutdownTime\": shutdownTime.Format(time.RFC3339),\n301: \t\t},\n302: \t}\n303: \n304: \tspecMap, found, err := unstructured.NestedMap(agentRuntime.Object, \"spec\", \"podTemplate\")\n305: \tif err != nil {\n306: \t\treturn nil, err\n307: \t}\n308: \tif found {\n309: \t\tspec[\"podTemplate\"] = specMap\n310: \t}\n311: \n312: \tports, _, _ := unstructured.NestedSlice(agentRuntime.Object, \"spec\", \"ports\")\n313: \tif len(ports) > 0 {\n314: \t\tspec[\"ports\"] = ports\n315: \t}\n316: \n317: \tcr.Object[\"spec\"] = spec\n318: \n319: \treturn cr, nil\n320: }\n321: \n322: func (sc *SandboxController) buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(codeInterpreter *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string, ports []interface{}) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error) {\n323: \tcr := &unstructured.Unstructured{}\n324: \tcr.SetAPIVersion(\"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\")\n325: \tcr.SetKind(\"Sandbox\")\n326: \tcr.SetName(sandboxName)\n327: \tcr.SetNamespace(namespace)\n328: \n329: \tcr.SetLabels(map[string]string{\n330: \t\tconstants.LabelManagedBy:    constants.LabelManagedByValue,\n331: \t\tconstants.LabelSessionID:    sessionID,\n332: \t\tconstants.LabelWorkloadName: workloadName,\n333: \t\tconstants.LabelSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n334: \t})\n335: \n336: \tcr.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n337: \t\tconstants.AnnotationIdleTimeout: \"15m\",\n338: \t})\n339: \n340: \tshutdownTime := time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour)\n341: \n342: \tspec := map[string]interface{}{\n343: \t\t\"replicas\": int64(1),\n344: \t\t\"lifecycle\": map[string]interface{}{\n345: \t\t\t\"shutdownTime\": shutdownTime.Format(time.RFC3339),\n346: \t\t},\n347: \t}\n348: \n349: \tif len(ports) > 0 {\n350: \t\tspec[\"ports\"] = ports\n351: \t}\n352: \n353: \timage, _, _ := unstructured.NestedString(codeInterpreter.Object, \"spec\", \"template\", \"image\")\n354: \tif image == \"\" {\n355: \t\timage = \"python:3.11-slim\"\n356: \t}\n357: \n358: \tcontainer := corev1.Container{\n359: \t\tName:  \"code-interpreter\",\n360: \t\tImage: image,\n361: \t}\n362: \n363: \tpodSpec := corev1.PodSpec{\n364: \t\tContainers: []corev1.Container{container},\n365: \t}\n366: \n367: \tpodSpecMap, err := runtime.DefaultUnstructuredConverter.ToUnstructured(&podSpec)\n368: \tif err != nil {\n369: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to convert pod spec: %w\", err)\n370: \t}\n371: \n372: \tspec[\"podTemplate\"] = podSpecMap\n373: \n374: \tcr.Object[\"spec\"] = spec\n375: \n376: \treturn cr, nil\n377: }\n378: \n379: func (sc *SandboxController) buildEntryPoints(podIP string, ports []interface{}) []api.EntryPoint {\n380: \tvar entryPoints []api.EntryPoint\n381: \tfor _, p := range ports {\n382: \t\tportMap, ok := p.(map[string]interface{})\n383: \t\tif !ok {\n384: \t\t\tcontinue\n385: \t\t}\n386: \n387: \t\tprotocol, _, _ := unstructured.NestedString(portMap, \"protocol\")\n388: \t\tport, _, _ := unstructured.NestedInt64(portMap, \"port\")\n389: \t\tpath, _, _ := unstructured.NestedString(portMap, \"pathPrefix\")\n390: \n391: \t\tif port == 0 || protocol == \"\" {\n392: \t\t\tcontinue\n393: \t\t}\n394: \n395: \t\tentryPoints = append(entryPoints, api.EntryPoint{\n396: \t\t\tProtocol: protocol,\n397: \t\t\tEndpoint: fmt.Sprintf(\"%s:%d\", podIP, port),\n398: \t\t\tPath:     path,\n399: \t\t\tPort:     int32(port),\n400: \t\t})\n401: \t}\n402: \treturn entryPoints\n403: }\n404: \n405: func convertEntryPoints(entryPoints []api.EntryPoint) []types.SandboxEntryPoint {\n406: \tvar result []types.SandboxEntryPoint\n407: \tfor _, ep := range entryPoints {\n408: \t\tresult = append(result, types.SandboxEntryPoint{\n409: \t\t\tProtocol: ep.Protocol,\n410: \t\t\tEndpoint: ep.Endpoint,\n411: \t\t\tPath:     ep.Path,\n412: \t\t})\n413: \t}\n414: \treturn result\n415: }\n416: \n417: func convertToAPIEntryPoints(entryPoints []types.SandboxEntryPoint) []api.EntryPoint {\n418: \tvar result []api.EntryPoint\n419: \tfor _, ep := range entryPoints {\n420: \t\tresult = append(result, api.EntryPoint{\n421: \t\t\tProtocol: ep.Protocol,\n422: \t\t\tEndpoint: ep.Endpoint,\n423: \t\t\tPath:     ep.Path,\n424: \t\t})\n425: \t}\n426: \treturn result\n427: }\n428: \n429: func generateSandboxName(workloadName string) string {\n430: \treturn fmt.Sprintf(\"%s-%s\", workloadName, RandString(8))\n431: }\n432: \n433: func RandString(n int) string {\n434: \tconst charset = \"abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789\"\n435: \tb := make([]byte, n)\n436: \tfor i := range b {\n437: \t\tb[i] = charset[rand.Intn(len(charset))]\n438: \t}\n439: \treturn string(b)\n440: }\n\n(End of file - total 440 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package controller\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"math/rand\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n\tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n\tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/constants\"\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\"\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/api\"\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/client\"\n)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go","time":{"start":1775845692293,"end":1775845692314}}}}
